<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Accustomed" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Accustomed,</orth> customary (used of things only): <cit><quote>her a. crossness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the a. sight of death,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 5, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your a. diligence,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his a. health,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an old a. feast,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 2, 20</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an a. action with her,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 32</bibl></cit>.
